      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "b0e5408fa2dad9dd",
      "text": "The project has been funded by the Kitchen Table Trust and the American Embassy. The further news is that although the money was given by the two organisations to build six toillets the money has been 'stretched' to build seven! It is heartening to hear that the money from these two donors has 'bought' even more than anticipated. This is the second piece of news."
    },
